title: [Yander's Farm, Barn]
description: The floor's chaff is damp toward the barn's northwest corner, and the walls display lines of dark discoloration.

The floor's chaff is damp toward the barn's northwest corner, and the walls display lines of dark discoloration.  The smell of mildew rises from the area, though it is faint and not overpowering at all.  Mice race about, searching for morsels of wheat that the threshers may have left behind.
